title: I Walk On A Road To Slay Enemies In My Way In Other World
alternative_titles: My Way of Killing Gods in Another World
My Path to Killing Gods in Another World
summary: I Walk On A Road To Slay Enemies In My Way In Other World The genius top student played games in an attempt to flirt with girls, but was struck by lightening on a rainy day and transported into the world of the game?! To survive here, he could only rely on himself. Surrounded by monsters and gods, full of dangers, can he still return to his own world and continue chasing girls?!
